<div style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700">Digital Queue</div>

<p>Digitial queuing system where the queue member receives tickets and updates in their phones as SMS messages.</p>
    
<p>Functions included:</p>

<ul>
<li>Add queue members.</li>
<li>Iterate through the queue.</li>
<li>Create QR code for customers to add themselves to the queue</li>
<li>Check current queue status</li>
<li>Visual presentation of your queue.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you want to send a link with the current queue status in your queue ticket message, contact our support team, who then will implement Pages-functionality.</p>

<p>Required for Pages-functionality:</p>

<ul>
<li>Change the token in the workflow: Incoming HTTP Trigger "pages_new" and message templates for "pages"</li>
<li>Change name of columns in service. Change to the chosen queue name.</li>
<li>Change the logo. Bosbec logo is deafult.</li>
</ul>

